原來你條傻鳩唔識中文衝出黎柒:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/324dmgopy7/Screenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F324dmgopy7%2FScreenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png&h=a28273a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>肥鳩大隻連解讀中文&ldquo;你照鏡咪知囉懵撚&rdquo;哩句句子都有困難，自己柒左仲要周圍話俾人知，不如學好d中文先出黎教人啦懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></span></span>"},{"pid":"c960e1d64094c1ea9445fcdc00ed747699090bbd","tid":470270,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻男人扮女人，鐵證如山，本癲狗發現左之後，知道原來自己係同緊一個變態人妖溝通，已懊悔不已，所以決定拆穿佢既罪行，免得各位受騙:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻曾經被一向撐開佢既契仔鄭俊弘 (宜家改左名叫鄭欣宜)同其他會員篤爆佢係肥佬扮女人:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s10.postimg.org/eq8erqgi1/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-54-22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs10.postimg.org%2Feq8erqgi1%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-54-22.png&h=99e1c7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/mhshwom03/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fmhshwom03%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png&h=2dcd081b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續去死撐啦，傻仔同快D用假膠黎掩飾啦傻鳩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573cfedf49e6c5758abc91c38e7921f5705e0da0","tid":470270,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5af37f48598789b8d735adbdac2e1fa2de40ae32","tid":470270,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文盲牛屎佬肥鳩大隻回覆親post呃正評都要趁連登各位巴打打錯字但自己卻打錯字，永遠都活喺本癲狗同連登各位巴打陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/wx6ks9uq1/1505721362017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fwx6ks9uq1%2F1505721362017.png&h=31f16109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係&ldquo;嘅&rdquo;，唔係&ldquo;既&rdquo;呀on9仔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔識字學人教中文正傻鳩，肥鳩大隻已被本癲狗完美KO</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52357959b32040617625354472a6621269a35639","tid":470270,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">肥鳩大隻乃連登論壇知名柒頭，經常誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，點知當佢同本癲狗正面交鋒就高下立見，睇下各位撐邊個多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/87fkcxet3j/1508057207119.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F87fkcxet3j%2F1508057207119.png&h=76fb8ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">咦? 肥鳩大隻，你想借本癲狗上位失敗wo，睇下我同你個post分別既支持度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上唔到位發爛咋呀傻鳩</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>再睇下你條本癲狗交鋒之下係輸得幾咁羞家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/5f5hw5g2un/1508057486497.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F5f5hw5g2un%2F1508057486497.png&h=c92bb693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/zzu52bwmn/1508057435505.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2Fzzu52bwmn%2F1508057435505.png&h=f091cd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由此可見，肥鳩大隻同本癲狗實力縣殊，想借本癲狗上位卻慘敗收場，因而只能作出零星而無力的反抗，反過來誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，其實本癲狗只係從容撚狗，已獲得大家支持</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同時亦證明左，無論肥鳩大隻花盡心機，唸盡辦法想同本癲狗玩，但換黎既結果只有慘敗同被撚，所以永遠活係本癲狗既陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6626752b5caaf585237b7e74ae7a96230faf0c04","tid":470270,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">當肥鳩大隻被拆穿其柒點時，就會以話自己&ldquo;假膠&rdquo;同話對方&ldquo;真心膠&rdquo;來為自己辯護，如下圖:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/huoj9jqeh/Screenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fhuoj9jqeh%2FScreenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png&h=0f10322e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜條傻鳩唔明白一個道理，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係明眼人一睇就知，肥鳩其實就係故事主角既投射</span></span></strong>，例如牠本身又肥又矮，就會引用d主角又肥又矮既故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>所以各位都爭相留下正皮，表示對其恥笑及支持本癲狗的撚狗行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b8104acba7282c1fdddd8e4d2be80370cee5262d","tid":470270,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">肥鳩大隻on9邏輯: 原來網上search到自己既身型就等如自己唔係肥佬<br />\n<br />\n小學畢左業先好衝出黎柒啦，係度做小丑娛賓俾本癲狗玩無撚用架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f186ebe592670b038c88b1c7f65358929e57b758","tid":470270,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bef0b147ba9fc23d5878652e318a8361027eb5e","tid":470270,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">癲狗廚子自家邏輯：上網求其搵張相=張相就係肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">肥鳩大隻on9邏輯: 原來網上search到自己既身型就等如自己唔係肥佬<br />\n<br />\n小學畢左業先好衝出黎柒啦，係度做小丑娛賓俾本癲狗玩無撚用架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"75fcc038b3025234b3d6337e875415747818955e","tid":470270,"uid":61765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/151608_97170daaeab7098f5216ce9d2370e88d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F151608_97170daaeab7098f